{"tid":2232560,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仲記唔記得15-20年前用手機sms真係會用曬字數上限？","createTime":"2020-10-06T12:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T12:34:42.000Z","uid":325200,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4eb6e8900f0728000bc00c63aa41ff2d406bdbb","tid":2232560,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"我會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩搵返部咸豐年代既Nokia機<br />\n睇返入邊同初戀既msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個陣唔知好似一個msg要收5毫<br />\n所以我個個msg都打足60-70隻字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中間仲夾雜住好多連登仔最憎既「吾」「牙」「系」<br />\n諗返都覺得又甜又酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成版sms紀錄曬由岩岩拍拖既甜言蜜語<br />\n到分手個陣嘈交大家屌黎屌去既msg<br />\n<br />\n好多野人大左 真係唔記得曬當年既甜酸苦辣...<br />\n眼前依部細細部既nokia就好似一部時光機咁<br />\n帶我再重新體驗一次初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有既記憶都返曬黎"},{"pid":"fc3cd30159bc0ea74991156102e4f748ba93da8d","tid":2232560,"uid":273932,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"當年溝女抄牌，對方第一句係問咩你咩台？唔同台就唔交換電話了。<br />\n<br />\n仲有同女朋友sms到要交千幾蚊電話費，誇鳩張<br />\n<br />\n回憶翻曬來"},{"pid":"836fdef98b7e4dc2cdfbd4da533e1a392eff8267","tid":2232560,"uid":77320,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:54:21.000Z","msg":"W810i<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好懷念<br />\n有冇YouTube片可以回味下"},{"pid":"35770e10e538373ca487ba4f72ca6290f298388f","tid":2232560,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc3cd30159bc0ea74991156102e4f748ba93da8d","tid":2232560,"uid":273932,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:52:49.000Z","msg":"當年溝女抄牌，對方第一句係問咩你咩台？唔同台就唔交換電話了。<br />\n<br />\n仲有同女朋友sms到要交千幾蚊電話費，誇鳩張<br />\n<br />\n回憶翻曬來"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06